---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Home"
  description="Charli.info is the public home of Charli-Jo Tyrer: a writer, conceptual artist and accessibility thinker working with AI and design fiction in public."
  type="WebSite"
>
  <h1>The public home of Charli-Jo Tyrer</h1>

  <p>I am a writer, conceptual artist and accessibility thinker working with generative AI, design fiction and agent-first digital systems.</p>
  <p>My work explores what happens when accessibility, AI and design fiction begin shaping the same future.</p>

  <div class="destinations">
    <section class="destination destination-art" aria-labelledby="blind-ant-heading">
      <h2 id="blind-ant-heading">Blind Ant</h2>
      <p>Blind Ant is my conceptual art practice, using generative AI as an artistic medium.</p>
      <p>Through design fiction, Blind Ant explores identity, disability, technology, power, care and the strange systems people build around themselves.</p>
      <p><a class="destination-link" href="/blind-ant/">Go to Blind Ant</a></p>
    </section>

    <section class="destination destination-access" aria-labelledby="carrados-heading">
      <h2 id="carrados-heading">Carrados</h2>
      <p>Carrados is my accessibility and agent-first design work. It explores how AI systems, websites and digital services can reduce informational suffering rather than reproduce it.</p>
      <p>Carrados is also home to Zero Information Casualty (ZIC), a design standard for preserving information across people, interfaces and intelligent agents.</p>
      <p><a class="destination-link" href="/carrados/">Go to Carrados</a></p>
    </section>

    <section class="destination" aria-labelledby="perspectives-heading">
      <h2 id="perspectives-heading">Perspectives</h2>
      <p>Long-form essays and propositions about the future, meaning and the responsibilities of being here.</p>
      <p><a class="destination-link" href="/perspectives/">Read the Perspectives</a></p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section aria-labelledby="together-with-heading">
    <h3 id="together-with-heading">Together With&hellip;</h3>
    <p>Courses, projects and other work made in collaboration with organisations and communities.</p>
    <p><a href="/together-with/tavip/confident-with-ai/">Confident with AI &mdash; with TAVIP</a></p>
  </section>

  <p class="closing-note">Read the site's <a href="/accessibility-statement/">Accessibility and Conformance Statement</a>.</p>
  <p class="closing-note">Everything on this site is published under a <a rel="license" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/">Creative Commons licence</a> unless otherwise stated.</p>
</Base>
